title: Diane kimmerle
text:
I had sent a birthday present to my parents, they loved the quantity and quality of what they received the instructions were easy to follow and they throughly enjoyed the meal
the prices were great, very competitive. I thought the shipping charges were a little high but after hearing about the quality it was worth it
